    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款1-5人联机的生存恐怖游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为《怪奇迷宫：第九批进入者》的序幕游戏，与第九批进入者相比，你将扮演第一批进入迷宫的人，你的线索更少，生存压力更大。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会在一片野生丛林中醒来，没有任何线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透过树叶的缝隙，他们可以看到自己被高墙包围着。城墙在黎明时打开，在夜间关闭。 你必须尽力收集足够的物资，并在这片相对安全的森林中建立自己的据点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/eb1312a9cbc813c2ebabdf1ecf11c424.poster.avif?t=1753970905\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/eb1312a9cbc813c2ebabdf1ecf11c424.webm?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/eb1312a9cbc813c2ebabdf1ecf11c424.mp4?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你做好充分准备后，进入充满未知危险的迷宫，收集更重要的材料，解决复杂的谜题，做出标记，并尝试尽可能地延伸你的足迹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/55dce729ffdd7fa0e3ebde893910c6bc.poster.avif?t=1753970905\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/55dce729ffdd7fa0e3ebde893910c6bc.webm?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/55dce729ffdd7fa0e3ebde893910c6bc.mp4?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但请记住，除非您做好充分准备，否则请在天黑之前逃到安全区域！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/7b7d18ed9359da2196b9ab89b91a0a0d.poster.avif?t=1753970905\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/7b7d18ed9359da2196b9ab89b91a0a0d.webm?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/7b7d18ed9359da2196b9ab89b91a0a0d.mp4?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >危险的黑暗区域会摧毁你的精神！怪物也会更加的狂暴！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而且能见度极低，让你行动困难！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迷宫背后似乎有一股神秘的力量影响着你的行动，不断地阻碍着你的行动。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >去吧，看看你是否能逃脱。如果不行，努力为后面的进入者留下更多的线索。</p>",
